---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog — Public Speaking & Communication Tips
description: Practical articles on public speaking, body language, voice, storytelling, charisma and communication — from theatre director and coach Viesturs Meikšāns.
---
<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 md:pt-20 pb-10 text-center">
  <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-500 mb-4">The ResonateKit Blog</p>
  <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight text-neutral-900 mb-5">Speak with <em class="text-[#E07B6A]">confidence &amp; impact</em></h1>
  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">Practical tips on public speaking, body language, voice, storytelling and communication — from theatre director and coach Viesturs Meikšāns.</p>
</header>

<!-- POSTS GRID -->
<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
{% for post in posts %}
    <a href="/blog/{{ post.slug }}/" class="group flex flex-col rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-neutral-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
      <div class="overflow-hidden aspect-video bg-neutral-100"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="{{ post.thumbnail }}" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/800x450/f5f0eb/3d2d5e?text={{ post.category | urlencode }}'" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" alt="{{ post.alt }}" /></div>
      <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-1"><p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-500 mb-2">{{ post.category }}</p><h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-neutral-900 leading-snug mb-2">{{ post.title }}</h2><p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed flex-1">{{ post.excerpt }}</p><span class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-700 group-hover:text-[#E07B6A] transition-colors">Read article<svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg></span></div>
    </a>
{% endfor %}
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="mt-16 rounded-3xl bg-[#3d2d5e] px-8 py-12 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight mb-4">Ready to work on it for real?</h2>
    <p class="text-white/70 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">Reading helps — but speaking skills are built with feedback. Explore 1:1 coaching and team training with Viesturs Meikšāns.</p>
    <a href="/#izveles" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl border border-black text-black text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-[#E07B6A] hover:text-white transition-colors" style="background:#8AE14A;">Explore the programs</a>
  </div>
</main>
